Doc: A description of the legal agreement(s) and definitions that document a party's relationships with other parties

Source.Contents:
/#
   A description of the legal agreement(s) and definitions that document a party's relationships with other parties
 #/
record FpML5.reporting.PartyRelationshipDocumentation {
  # A agreement executed between two parties that includes or references the related party.
  masterAgreement : FpML5.reporting.MasterAgreement

  # An agreement executed between two parties intended to govern collateral arrangement for OTC derivatives transactions between those parties, and that references the related party.
  creditSupportAgreement : FpML5.reporting.CreditSupportAgreement

  # An agrement that references the related party.
  agreement : FpML5.reporting.GenericAgreement

}

masterAgreement.Doc: A agreement executed between two parties that includes or references the related party.
masterAgreement.Name: masterAgreement

creditSupportAgreement.Doc: An agreement executed between two parties intended to govern collateral arrangement for OTC derivatives transactions between those parties, and that references the related party.
creditSupportAgreement.Name: creditSupportAgreement

agreement.Doc: An agrement that references the related party.
agreement.Name: agreement
